      RUFOUGABUPCDAUOCURLUIUJUK $.
      $( [6-Dec-2000] $)

    $( The orthomodular law.  Remark in [Kalmbach] p. 22. $)
    pjoml5i $p |- ( A vH ( ( _|_ ` A ) i^i ( A vH B ) ) ) = ( A vH B ) $=
