    $( Comparable Hilbert lattice elements commute.  Theorem 2.3(iii) of
       [Beran] p. 40. $)
    lecmi $p |- ( A C_ B -> A C_H B ) $=
      ( wss cort cfv chj co cin ccm wbr ssinss1 cmbr4i sylibr ) ABEAAFGBHIZJBEA
